peavine capital  investment management peavine capital manages over  million and was founded in  by ken lambert ken has over two decades of investment experience including serving as chief investment officer for the  billion nevada public employees retirement system   during his tenure as leader of nevada pers investment program the funds performance ranked in the top  of public pension plans peavine capital gives investors access to the strategy ken used to generate institutional results   we don’t just manage assets we provide experienced investment leadership this includes a unique combination of portfolio construction decisive action and clear communication our goal is to give investors the confidence to stay the course through volatile markets     contact peavine capital llc is a registered investment adviser the views expressed are those of peavine capital and are subject to change information taken from sources deemed to be reliable ken lambert served as chief investment officer of nevada pers june  through march  and investment strategist march  through  pers’ performance ranking statistics for the period june  through june  based on callan associates’ database of public pension plans with more than  billion in assets pers’ return ranking for that period is th percentile and risk adjusted return ranking is th percentile nevada pers’ results are not indicative of past or future performance generated by peavine capital not a solicitation to buy nor offer to sell securities past performance is no guarantee of future returns investing involves risk and possible loss of principal investment advisory services offered through peavine capital llc advisory services are only offered to clients or prospective clients where peavine capital llc and its representatives are properly licensed or exempt from licensure custody and other brokerage services provided to direct clients of peavine capital llc are offered by fidelity brokerage services llc member nysesipc peavine c