the cfa institute is to lead the investment profession globally by promoting the highest standards of ethics education and professional excellence for the ultimate benefit of society member current chartered alternative investment analyst association the caia association a nonprofit organization founded in  is the world leader and authority in alternative investment education the fundamentals of alternative investments certificate program® is a natural extension of caia’s mission to provide solutions to specific market needs for alternative investment education the caia association is best known for the caia charter® an internationally recognized credential granted upon successful completion of a rigorous twolevel exam series combined with relevant work experience earning the caia charter is the gateway to becoming a member of the caia association a global network of  alternative investment leaders located in  countries who have demonstrated a deep and thorough understanding of alternative investing career history chief investment officer   current peavine capital llc peavine capital llc is a private company headquartered in reno nv that provides investment advice the firm was founded in  by kenneth bruce lambert he has been the ceo since that date consultantpeavine capital management prior public employees retirement system of nevada the public employees retirement system of nevadas pers investment program is designed to capture the power of compound interest to meet those benefit obligations while minimizing risk pers retirement board has implemented an investment strategy that maximizes riskadjusted return to meet these funding requirements their investment approach is based on maintaining a consistent exposure to the capital markets using a disciplined rebalancing program to buy assets at lower prices and sell them at higher prices and keeping costs low pers strategy is broadly diversified and emphasizes high quality assets the fund is invested in over  securities to ensure any individual asset will not have an undue influence on total portfolio risk they utilize a rebalancing system to keep the portfolio inline with its policy targets pers investments include us stocks international stocks us bonds international bonds and investments in private markets executive vice president prior ledson development executive vice president prior ledson winery and vineyards boards  committees nonprofit boards ▾ chairman prior national association of state investment officers awards  honors professional certification cfa chartered financial analyst sponsored by cfa institute professional certification chartered alternative investment analyst richard l rosenthal award sponsored by new york university  leonard n stern school of business other affiliations kenneth bruce lambert is affiliated with peavine capital llc public employees retirement system of nevada ledson development ledson winery and vineyards national association of state investment officers youve reached your  free profiles limit this month upgrade to relsci pro today to enjoy unlimited article views and much more start my free trial ➤ still not convinced check out our full listing of features here are you a relsci pro subscriber login to relsci pro  ➤ not a pro subscriber log in here to manage your alerts keep me signed in login  ➤ forgot your password i have read the lexisnexis terms  conditions sign me up  ➤ kenneth bruce lambert  financial advisor reno nv  brightscope advisor pages getsearchtypedisplaynamesearchtype advisor funds firms k plans back to top homeadvisor pageskenneth bruce lambert kenneth bruce lambertfind an advisor overviewservicesfundsqualificationsarticleslicensesassetsfees is this youclaim this profile share follow following kenneth bruce lambert peavine capital llc reno nvfind an advisor overviewservicesfundsqualificationsarticleslicensesassetsfees overview description kenneth lambert is an executive and is the majority owner of peavine capital llc a m 